name: Kawalan
description:
'Kawalan'(nothingness) is the term used by the creator to define the word 'Space'. He started exploring space in 1997. We see space as if it is empty or nothing's in there. But for sure, that’s not the reality of the creator. 
Some strips may look alike but in every space, the creator guaranteed that there will be no totally identical strips/pieces. Like humans living in this space. Every existence has its own 
color, shape, energy, aura, and beauty!

KAWALAN-03
